BACKGROUND	O
ART	O
Prior	O
art	O
interactive	O
spoken	O
dialogue	O
systems	O
and	O
methods	O
have	O
generally	O
focused	O
on	O
understanding	O
a	O
spoken	O
command	O
or	O
sentence	O
in	O
