to	O
perform	O
desired	O
tasks	O
.	O
Such	O
systems	O
are	O
disclosed	O
by	O
Best	O
in	O
U.S.	O
Pat	O
.	O
No.	O
4	O
,	O
569	O
,	O
026	O
,	O
Kimura	O
et	O
al	O
in	O
U.S.	O
Pat	O
.	O
No.	O
5	O
,	O
247	O
,	O
580	O
,	O
and	O
Douglas	O
in	O
U.S.	O
Pat	O
.	O
No.	O
5	O
,	O
335	O
,	O
313	O
.	O
Typically	O
,	O
these	O
systems	O
first	O
try	O
to	O
distinguish	O
every	O
word	O
in	O
an	O
utterance	O
,	O
i	O
.	O
e	O
.	O
a	O
user	O
command	O
.	O
Each	O
